{"tid":483383,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[失物post] 地鐵有金執","createTime":"2017-11-29T05:37:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-29T07:16:30.000Z","uid":144260,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"12a690b7a74f7ec5237c2509bcb7825fa428d9b6","tid":483383,"uid":144260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T05:37:48.000Z","msg":"其實唔係金 係SD card<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今朝搭地鐵 跌左張SD card<br />\n(普通相機卡 唔係micro SD )<br />\n我由觀塘搭去灣仔 喺油塘同北角轉過車<br />\n最大機會喺油塘或者北角月台跌<br />\n<br />\n我知係自己唔小心 鞭屍手下留情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求各位途徑呢幾個地鐵站嘅巴絲得閒望下地下 如果咁啱見到細細張黑色嘅野 應該就係我張SD card <br />\n<br />\n希望有心人可以交去地鐵客戶服務或者pm我 連登有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"460983c30b968ef59b550a29b53186ef9ecb499b","tid":483383,"uid":144260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T05:58:52.000Z","msg":"退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d2f7bc40b25ab41298f4326bc95046d9c30457f","tid":483383,"uid":144260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T05:59:21.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20821d3341db54c92f36ad613aa59e773b96d971","tid":483383,"uid":144260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T05:59:49.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91029f573b53e0907a85f1e7f8485b264f3a0088","tid":483383,"uid":144260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T06:00:03.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ddde550fa6bf6b3691ccc31dcf6e18d3117f846","tid":483383,"uid":6329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T06:00:46.000Z","msg":"一陣搭地鐵幫你留意下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b03e0fa84d0f82cf8d5399